Class SeleniumEventLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.concordion.cubano.driver.web.SeleniumEventLogger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.openqa.selenium.support.events.WebDriverEventListener

    public class SeleniumEventLogger
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.openqa.selenium.support.events.WebDriverEventListener

    Listens for WebDriver events and logs them.

    Requires Selenium 2.23.0 or later to retrieve element names from WebElement.toString().
